description:
This package is merged into main Docotic.Pdf package. Switch to https://www.nuget.org/packages/BitMiracle.Docotic.Pdf/ and enable "Include Prerelease" option to use latest developer builds. 

How to enable "Include Prerelease" option: https://docs.nuget.org/create/versioning#installing-prerelease-packages

---

This is the Beta version of Docotic.Pdf library.
		
		Beta version contains newest features and latest bug fixes. This version is tested for regressions and is safe to be used in production environment.
		
		Release version can be found here: https://www.nuget.org/packages/BitMiracle.Docotic.Pdf/.
		
		Docotic.Pdf library can create, edit, draw and print PDF files.

The library is a fully managed assembly for .NET 2.0 and later frameworks. The assembly has no external dependencies.

There are different types of licenses: for applications, for servers, cloud and unlimited. All licenses are royalty-free. 

Free time-limited licenses are available upon request.
